<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Apr1939"><font color="red">28 April 1939</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter telling me that Mr Joyce has moved to his new address &mdash; and enclosing a copy of the letter you were sending to the amazing person in the USA who wanted to publish part of Mr Joyce&apos;s earliest manuscripts of &ldquo;A Portrait of the Artist&rdquo; &hellip; I received two days ago from Messrs Faber and Faber an advance copy. The book seems to me very well produced &mdash; after this long time. </div>
